SUMMARY:St George's Day Parade
DESCRIPTION:The whole Group joins our District for the annual St George&amp\;rsquo\;s Day Parade. Meet at Anytown Parish Church for inspection at 09:30\, then we march to the war memorial for the act of remembrance and the Scout promise.\nParents are very welcome to come along and watch.\n
